long_description: located in rosenberg, tx. paveloc is a private company categorized under paving equipment manufacturers. established in 2007 and incorporated in texas, led by ceo ted gillis and his ever growing staff of skilled employees, ted is a college educated man who is always willing to get his hands dirty instead of staying static behind a desk. we here at paveloc, manufacture pavestones and concrete retaining walls, and also feature the thindek system. our products offer an alternative to traditional concrete or asphalt pavements, plus the promise of enhanced structural and cost benefits. here at paveloc our focus is bringing the greatest quality grade of materials to our clients so that you may manifest your dream homes into reality.
